'''Salaam Namaste 90.4''' is the first [[community radio]] station of [[Noida]] and [[Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh|Ghaziabad]]. The tag line of the radio is Radio that Listens. It is based at campus of IMS Noida. 

==Objective==
The prime objective of Salaam Namaste 90.4 is to educate the community through interactive programmes. Salaam Namaste is by the community and for the community.

