'''United Defense Manufacturing Corporation''' ('''UDMC''') is a Philippine defense contractor and [[firearm]]s manufacturer based in [[Parañaque]], [[Philippines]]. It provides the [[Philippine National Police]], [[Armed Forces of the Philippines]], and [[Philippine Coast Guard]], amongst others, with firearms and other tactical equipment.<ref>{{cite web|title=ABOUT US -- United Defense Manufacturing Corporation|url=http://www.udmc-weapons.com/aboutus.php|accessdate=13 June 2012}}</ref>
The company primarily produces [[M1911]]-pattern pistols and [[AR-15]]-pattern rifles and carbines, notably producing a gas-piston variant called the '''Pneumatic Valve and Rod Assault Rifle (PVAR)'''.<ref>{{cite web|title=PRODUCTS -- United Defense Manufacturing Corporation|url=http://www.udmc-weapons.com/products.php|accessdate=13 June 2012}}</ref>
